        <summary>How long is Shadows Awaken Chapter 1?</summary>
        <div>Chapter 1 is a focused experience set in a two-story house. The gameplay involves finding nine ghosts while managing light, anxiety, and avoiding Freddy across increasingly intense phases, culminating in a high-pressure red-lit finale.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary>Will there be more chapters?</summary>
        <div>Yes, the game is episodic. Chapter 2 (described as the Bonnie chapter) is planned, with the possibility of additional chapters beyond that. The developer Kyesen continues to post development updates.</div>
